WEBVTT

01:35.679 --> 01:37.879
God, I Hate
Those Stupid Jerks

01:37.880 --> 01:40.666
And Their Fucking
Boarding School.

01:40.667 --> 01:42.835
And All Their
Stupid Sermons.

01:45.105 --> 01:47.672
That Fucking Slut Is
Going To Banish Us Again.

01:47.673 --> 01:49.474
Are You Crazy, Zoe?

01:49.475 --> 01:51.476
How Can You
Call Her That?

01:51.477 --> 01:53.846
She--She's A Nun.

01:55.531 --> 01:57.466
[Girls Laughing
And Chattering]

02:01.571 --> 02:03.905
Watch Out! I Think
The Bitch Is Coming.

02:12.749 --> 02:15.367
Ms. Eulalia Esteve,

02:15.368 --> 02:17.252
Your Pathetic Limp

02:17.253 --> 02:19.905
Is No Excuse
Not To Be Seated.

02:24.177 --> 02:26.778
It's God's Punishment.

02:26.779 --> 02:29.431
All Your Other Teachers
Have Told Me

02:29.432 --> 02:32.684
That Your Behavior
Gets Worse Every Day.

02:34.604 --> 02:37.756
Your Disobedience
And Lack Of Respect

02:37.757 --> 02:39.591
Are Unacceptable.

02:41.227 --> 02:44.229
This Institution
Will Not Allow You

02:44.230 --> 02:47.149
To Stray
Beyond The Limits.

02:47.150 --> 02:50.435
Your Parents Have
Entrusted Me With...

02:50.436 --> 02:51.887
A Mission.

02:53.156 --> 02:54.940
That's Why
They Brought You

02:54.941 --> 02:56.641
From Your
Respective Countries

02:56.642 --> 02:58.059
To This Boarding School.

02:59.729 --> 03:02.164
They Wanted To Keep
You Away From Sin.

03:03.682 --> 03:07.485
And I Shall Fulfill
My Responsibilities...

03:07.486 --> 03:09.921
In Spite Of You.

03:11.591 --> 03:15.310
Joanna, Mary,

03:15.311 --> 03:18.496
Christine, Eulalia,

03:18.497 --> 03:21.817
Zoe, Susan...

03:21.818 --> 03:25.204
All Of You Young Ladies
Have Christian Names--

03:25.205 --> 03:27.956
Names Of Saints
And Holy Women.

03:27.957 --> 03:30.826
All Of Them Suffered
Martyrdom,

03:30.827 --> 03:33.445
Torture, And Pain.

03:33.446 --> 03:36.281
They Taught Us
That Sacrifice

03:36.282 --> 03:38.833
Brings Us
Closer To God

03:38.834 --> 03:41.603
And To Perfection.

03:41.604 --> 03:43.505
And Keeps Us From Sin.

03:43.506 --> 03:46.825
And Worthy Of
Being Reunited

03:46.826 --> 03:49.328
With The Almighty.

04:16.372 --> 04:17.971
A Love Letter!

04:19.225 --> 04:23.495
Ms. Mary O'brien...

04:23.496 --> 04:24.713
Don't You Know

04:24.714 --> 04:27.382
That Love Can
Bring About Sin?

04:28.551 --> 04:31.019
Ms. Mary O'brien,

04:31.020 --> 04:32.604
Open Your Mouth.

04:34.507 --> 04:36.508
Open Your Mouth!

04:36.509 --> 04:37.993
Ugh.

04:37.994 --> 04:39.428
Uhh.

04:39.429 --> 04:41.279
Swallow It!

04:48.838 --> 04:50.772
Ugh!

04:50.773 --> 04:53.758
Only Pain Can
Wash Away Our Sins!

04:53.759 --> 04:54.776
Ugh!

04:56.296 --> 04:57.445
Aah!

05:01.084 --> 05:02.233
Aah!

05:02.234 --> 05:03.452
Ahh!

05:30.763 --> 05:32.697
[Lively Music Playing]

05:50.116 --> 05:52.451
Hey, Joel.

05:52.452 --> 05:54.853
Aren't You Ever
Going To Let Go

05:54.854 --> 05:56.654
Of That Goddamn Camera?

05:56.655 --> 05:59.291
Whoa, Hey, I'm
The Lord Of The Films.

05:59.292 --> 06:03.095
And, Uh, This Is Julia...

06:03.096 --> 06:05.464
The Beautiful Spanish Girl

06:05.465 --> 06:07.799
I'm Going On Holiday
With This Summer.

06:10.587 --> 06:12.103
Hey, Joel,
Have You Seen Eve?

06:12.104 --> 06:14.373
Eve? Oh, Come On Artie,
Just Give It Up!

06:14.374 --> 06:15.908
With All The Girls There--

06:15.909 --> 06:18.143
Hey, Man, You Know
I Like A Challenge.

06:18.144 --> 06:20.579
She's Just Got Something
The Others Don't.

06:20.580 --> 06:21.363
You Know What I Mean?

06:21.364 --> 06:22.514
Do You Really
Think She's Still--

06:22.515 --> 06:23.499
Well, Ask Julia.

06:23.500 --> 06:25.967
Or Even Better,
Give Her The Lake Test.

06:25.968 --> 06:27.286
Hey, Lake?

06:27.287 --> 06:29.822
Joel, I Don't
Even Like Water.

06:29.823 --> 06:31.956
It's Cold.

06:31.957 --> 06:35.310
And The Water Is Muddy...

06:35.311 --> 06:37.596
Dirty...

06:37.597 --> 06:40.599
And There Is
Something Moving

06:40.600 --> 06:43.618
Like Snakes.

06:43.619 --> 06:44.802
I Told You,
It Never Fails.

06:44.803 --> 06:45.787
What?

06:49.308 --> 06:52.227
I Can't Go To Spain.

06:52.228 --> 06:55.514
All The Two Of You Ever
Think About Is Scuba Diving,

06:55.515 --> 06:57.249
And I'm Not Into That.

06:57.250 --> 06:58.967
I Always Wanted
To See Spain.

06:58.968 --> 07:00.185
What Are You Saying?

07:00.186 --> 07:01.719
You Always
Thought Spain

07:01.720 --> 07:03.822
Was In The
South Of Mexico.

07:03.823 --> 07:07.141
Anyway, My Mom Is Already
Going To Spain.

07:07.142 --> 07:10.078
And Her Being As She Is,

07:10.079 --> 07:11.713
The Last Thing
I Want To Do

07:11.714 --> 07:13.715
Is Go To Europe
And Bump Into Her.

07:19.071 --> 07:21.139
Hey, You Could
Leave The Camera

07:21.140 --> 07:23.142
Once And For All
To Dance A Little With Me,

07:23.143 --> 07:24.493
Don't You Think?

07:27.230 --> 07:29.848
Dancing?
Or Something More?

07:31.533 --> 07:35.020
And By The Way, I Haven't
Seen Eve For A While.

07:35.021 --> 07:37.655
Let's Hope She Finally--

07:37.656 --> 07:40.075
This Is Easy
To Find Out.

07:44.280 --> 07:45.914
Let's Find That Girl.

07:45.915 --> 07:48.033
She's Just Turned 18.

07:50.069 --> 07:52.237
Let's Find Out
If She Finally Goes

07:52.238 --> 07:53.671
For A Swim In The Lake.

08:01.430 --> 08:02.381
Oh!

08:10.890 --> 08:12.206
Aah!

08:33.279 --> 08:34.979
[Faint Thumping]

08:36.799 --> 08:38.332
Eve?

09:05.478 --> 09:06.594
[Thud]

09:20.993 --> 09:22.960
[Water Trickling]

09:28.851 --> 09:30.785
[Water Dripping]

09:32.555 --> 09:34.272
[Pipes Groaning]

09:36.275 --> 09:37.459
[Groaning Stops]

10:01.567 --> 10:03.485
[Water Sloshing]

10:12.578 --> 10:14.779
Eve, Is That You?

10:48.764 --> 10:50.431
Eve?

10:50.432 --> 10:52.183
Is Anyone There?

13:17.429 --> 13:18.680
Aah!

13:44.957 --> 13:46.874
[Distorted Voices]

14:19.475 --> 14:20.491
Aah!

14:23.112 --> 14:24.262
Aah!

14:24.263 --> 14:26.364
[Roars]

14:29.484 --> 14:30.602
Mom?

14:40.079 --> 14:41.813
Mom?

14:41.814 --> 14:44.349
Get Out Of Here!

15:00.683 --> 15:02.684
[Police Radio Chatter]

15:13.028 --> 15:15.029
Man: What Did
He Look Like, Eve?

15:15.030 --> 15:17.198
It Was Very Dark.

15:17.199 --> 15:19.834
Would You Recognize
Him Again?

15:19.835 --> 15:23.771
Whoever It Was
Was Wearing

15:23.772 --> 15:27.792
Something Like
A Black Hood, And...

15:29.061 --> 15:33.214
It Kind Of Looked
A Bit Like...

15:33.215 --> 15:36.784
Like A...A Nun.

15:39.388 --> 15:42.540
Your--Your Father,
Where's He?

15:42.541 --> 15:45.392
I Don't Know My Father.

15:45.393 --> 15:47.045
I See. Would You Have
Any Other Relatives?

15:47.046 --> 15:48.780
Ahem.
No.

15:50.916 --> 15:52.634
Excuse Me.

15:54.570 --> 15:56.404
Cut On Her
Throat's Clean.

15:56.405 --> 15:58.505
There's No Doubt It's
The Cause Of Death.

16:00.059 --> 16:02.060
So Far We Haven't Found
Any Fingerprints

16:02.061 --> 16:04.095
Except Those
Of The Victim.

16:04.096 --> 16:05.413
Ok, Thanks.

16:11.920 --> 16:13.587
I'm Here.

16:13.588 --> 16:15.173
[Sobbing]

16:19.745 --> 16:21.579
I'm Here.

16:21.580 --> 16:23.214
Excuse Me, Ladies.

16:27.436 --> 16:28.769
Look, I Promise You

16:28.770 --> 16:30.254
You're Going To Be
Out Of Here Real Soon.

16:30.255 --> 16:32.590
Uh, If She Is
Going To Stay With You,

16:32.591 --> 16:34.291
Then We're Going To Have

16:34.292 --> 16:35.443
To Have All Your Personal
Details. Ok?

16:35.444 --> 16:37.128
No Problem.
Thanks.

16:37.129 --> 16:38.897
Well, If You'd
Like To Come With Me,

16:38.898 --> 16:40.965
I'll Get Someone
To Write Them Down.

16:40.966 --> 16:42.801
I'll Be Right Back.

16:42.802 --> 16:44.051
Ok?

16:46.455 --> 16:48.490
Excuse Me, Sir?
Yeah.

16:48.491 --> 16:50.291
Well...

16:50.292 --> 16:53.678
Tell Me What's The Matter.

16:53.679 --> 16:55.663
Do You Think She
Committed Suicide?

16:55.664 --> 16:57.948
What Are You
Talking About?

16:57.949 --> 17:01.052
Eve's Mother Tried To
Kill Herself Years Ago.

17:01.053 --> 17:02.954
My Boyfriend Told Me.

17:02.955 --> 17:05.223
They've Been Friends
Since They Were Kids.

17:05.223 --> 17:09.260
Eve Was Only
3 Or 4 Years Old.

17:09.261 --> 17:11.028
And She Found Her Mother
In The Bathtub.

17:11.029 --> 17:12.313
To Tell You The Truth,

17:12.314 --> 17:14.482
I Think She Doesn't
Remember Very Well.

17:14.483 --> 17:17.050
According
To Psychologists,

17:17.051 --> 17:19.804
She Only Remembers That
Her Mother Was Very Sick.

17:21.323 --> 17:24.175
There Was Alcohol At The Party
Tonight, Wasn't There?

17:24.175 --> 17:25.693
Yeah, We All
Had A Few Drinks.

17:26.845 --> 17:28.713
Well, A Lot.

17:31.050 --> 17:32.717
What Are You Thinking?

17:32.718 --> 17:34.435
Who Knows?

17:34.436 --> 17:38.339
Perhaps Nobody Was There.

17:38.340 --> 17:41.008
Perhaps All We Have
Is Just A Very

17:41.009 --> 17:42.126
Confused Young Girl.

18:23.652 --> 18:25.270
Mambi!

18:27.890 --> 18:29.173
Mambi!

18:32.927 --> 18:34.495
Hey, Mambi!

18:36.315 --> 18:38.616
[Speaking Spanish]

18:41.737 --> 18:43.171
[Telephone Rings]

18:45.057 --> 18:46.757
[Ring]

18:46.758 --> 18:48.593
[Speaks Spanish]

18:48.594 --> 18:49.944
Zoe.

18:53.698 --> 18:56.484
Have You Spoken To Cristy?

18:56.485 --> 18:58.035
Now?

18:59.154 --> 19:00.754
Don't You Know
What's Happened?

19:07.429 --> 19:10.748
Cristy Called Me
From New York.

19:10.749 --> 19:13.084
She Had To Meet Mary.

19:13.085 --> 19:15.869
'Cause They Were Going
To Come Over Together.

19:17.773 --> 19:19.941
But They Didn't
Get To See Each Other.

19:22.377 --> 19:23.861
Mary's Dead, Too.

19:25.664 --> 19:28.099
We'll Wait For You.

19:28.100 --> 19:29.550
Have A Good Flight.

19:30.736 --> 19:32.703
[Church Bell Ringing]

19:42.981 --> 19:44.983
Eve: Thank You
For Staying.

19:44.984 --> 19:47.585
What Are Friends For?

19:47.586 --> 19:50.471
I Have To Go
Back To Spain.

19:50.472 --> 19:53.824
I Don't Want You
To Stay Here All Alone.

19:53.825 --> 19:55.409
Come With Us.

19:59.314 --> 20:00.965
Ok.

20:00.966 --> 20:03.067
I'll Wait For You
In The Car.

20:11.994 --> 20:13.911
You Look A Lot
Like Your Mother.

20:16.465 --> 20:18.182
I'm Sorry To Meet You

20:18.183 --> 20:20.318
Under These
Circumstances, Eve.

20:20.319 --> 20:23.504
I'm Cristy--
Cristy Keen.

20:23.505 --> 20:26.657
And I Was A Friend
Of Your Mother's.

20:26.658 --> 20:28.109
You Knew My Mother?

20:31.029 --> 20:33.747
We Hadn't Seen Each
Other For Many Years.

20:33.748 --> 20:36.935
I Live
On The West Coast.

20:36.936 --> 20:39.603
But We Were Going
On A Trip Together

20:39.604 --> 20:40.855
The Day After Tomorrow.

20:42.924 --> 20:44.892
She Said That Was
A Business Trip.

20:44.893 --> 20:46.894
We Had To Meet
Some Old Friends

20:46.895 --> 20:48.379
From Boarding School.

20:48.380 --> 20:50.181
The Catholic
Boarding School In Europe?

20:52.067 --> 20:54.985
She'd Never
Talk About That.

20:54.986 --> 20:56.236
A Week Ago, Joanna--

20:56.237 --> 20:57.738
Another Classmate--

20:57.739 --> 20:58.923
Also Died.

20:58.924 --> 21:00.341
In London.

21:02.210 --> 21:03.894
The Police--
They Don't Believe Me.

21:03.895 --> 21:06.514
They Say There Were
No Fingerprints.

21:08.417 --> 21:09.934
'Cause...

21:09.935 --> 21:13.254
They Say That She
Committed Suicide.

21:13.255 --> 21:16.773
But...
I Saw Someone.

21:18.093 --> 21:21.078
I'll Still Be In
The City Tomorrow, Eve.

21:21.079 --> 21:22.680
I Need To Speak To You.

22:12.314 --> 22:14.314
"Dear Mary,
Perhaps It Is True

22:14.315 --> 22:16.083
That Love Is Impossible."

22:17.986 --> 22:21.905
"And For Us,
Even More So.

22:21.906 --> 22:25.159
"I Love You
And Always Will.

22:25.160 --> 22:26.928
Miguel."

22:30.649 --> 22:32.517
Miguel?

22:35.671 --> 22:39.156
Ok, Eulalia,
I'll See You In Barcelona.

22:39.157 --> 22:41.325
Take Care.

22:41.326 --> 22:42.476
Bye.

23:20.198 --> 23:21.899
Eulalia?

23:24.536 --> 23:27.488
Barcelona. July 10th.

24:12.584 --> 24:13.200
Aah!

24:24.996 --> 24:26.446
Hello?

24:26.447 --> 24:28.949
Hello?

24:28.950 --> 24:30.784
Can You Hear Me?

24:30.785 --> 24:32.720
[Screams]

24:46.484 --> 24:48.235
[Muffled As If Underwater]
Is Anybody There?

24:56.978 --> 24:58.579
[Ghostly Sigh]

25:01.083 --> 25:03.250
Help Me!

25:16.297 --> 25:17.414
[Elevator Dings]

25:42.290 --> 25:43.440
[Ghostly Sigh]

25:54.670 --> 25:56.353
[Telephones Ringing]

26:16.424 --> 26:18.375
[Panting And Sobbing]

26:18.376 --> 26:20.728
[Creaking]

26:22.414 --> 26:23.697
Aah!

26:35.427 --> 26:37.261
[Elevator Dings]

26:37.262 --> 26:38.545
[Gasps]

26:41.833 --> 26:43.150
Oh!

26:45.387 --> 26:47.254
There's Been
An Accident!

26:47.255 --> 26:48.572
An Accident!

26:48.573 --> 26:49.790
[Elevator Dings]

26:59.801 --> 27:01.285
Eve, Come On.

27:01.286 --> 27:03.053
This Trip
Is For You To Relax

27:03.054 --> 27:05.656
And Try
To Forget Everything.

27:05.657 --> 27:08.776
I Have To Go To The
Boarding School Archives.

27:08.777 --> 27:10.227
Maybe In
One Of The Yearbooks

27:10.228 --> 27:12.062
I Could Find
Eulalia's Last Name,

27:12.063 --> 27:14.498
And Then I Could
Find Her Address.

27:14.499 --> 27:16.133
But That
Wasn't The Deal.

27:16.134 --> 27:18.051
Even The Police
Psychologist Said So.

27:20.806 --> 27:22.939
You Don't Believe Me,
Either, Do You?

27:38.256 --> 27:40.157
The Psychologist Said...

27:40.158 --> 27:42.626
That Sometimes...

27:42.627 --> 27:45.913
In Cases Like This,
The Mind...

27:45.914 --> 27:47.448
Plays Tricks On Us.

27:47.449 --> 27:49.132
Cristy Did Believe Me,

27:49.133 --> 27:51.819
And She Had Something
Very Important To Tell Me.

27:51.820 --> 27:53.737
There Wasn't A Nun
In The Hotel, Either.

27:53.738 --> 27:54.988
Yeah, But--

27:54.989 --> 27:58.325
The Police Told You.

27:58.326 --> 28:01.028
It Was An Accident.

28:01.029 --> 28:03.164
Eve, It's All Over.

28:03.165 --> 28:05.832
Do You Think That They'd
Let You Leave If It Wasn't?

28:05.833 --> 28:08.352
I Have
To Speak To Them.

28:08.353 --> 28:11.338
[Sighs] That Meeting
Is Tomorrow.

28:11.339 --> 28:13.674
Right?

28:13.675 --> 28:15.358
Yes.

28:15.359 --> 28:17.494
Ok.

28:17.495 --> 28:19.630
I'll Go With You.

28:19.631 --> 28:22.215
You'll Talk
To That Woman...

28:22.216 --> 28:24.785
And Then We'll
Go To The South,

28:24.786 --> 28:26.436
To The Beach.

28:28.606 --> 28:31.391
I'm Dying
To Get To Seville.

28:31.392 --> 28:33.326
I Bet You'll Love It.

28:33.327 --> 28:35.529
And You'll Also
Love My Friends,

28:35.530 --> 28:37.965
And I'm Sure You'll Find
Someone That You'll Like

28:37.966 --> 28:40.584
Better Than Harley.

28:40.585 --> 28:41.802
That Jerk!

28:59.286 --> 29:01.221
[Woman Sobbing
On Television]

29:26.080 --> 29:27.681
[Thunder]

29:51.939 --> 29:53.540
[Screams]

30:19.467 --> 30:20.651
Aah!

30:20.652 --> 30:22.135
Eve, Wake Up!

30:22.136 --> 30:23.453
Woman On P.A.:
Ladies And Gentlemen,

30:23.454 --> 30:25.322
We Will Shortly
Be Arriving In Barcelona.

30:25.323 --> 30:27.090
We're In Barcelona.

30:27.091 --> 30:30.477
Look How Beautiful
The City Is From Up Here.

30:30.478 --> 30:32.579
[Spanish Music Playing]

30:40.471 --> 30:42.439
[Singing In Spanish]

31:33.807 --> 31:35.542
Eulalia...

31:35.543 --> 31:37.878
Esteven.

31:37.879 --> 31:39.096
Esteven.

31:53.528 --> 31:56.713
[Speaking Spanish]

31:56.714 --> 31:59.832
Sorry?
I Don't Speak Spanish.

31:59.833 --> 32:01.367
Where You From?

32:01.368 --> 32:03.220
New York.

32:03.221 --> 32:05.055
Listen,
You Want To Make

32:05.056 --> 32:07.124
Some Photocopies,
Just Go Ahead

32:07.125 --> 32:09.910
Because I Still
Have Lots To Do.

32:09.911 --> 32:11.595
Thanks.

32:23.358 --> 32:25.658
Why Are You Interested
In This Boarding School?

32:25.659 --> 32:27.010
Do You Want
To Study There?

32:28.229 --> 32:29.763
Yeah.

32:29.764 --> 32:33.583
Well, It Says It's
Been Closed Since 1988.

32:33.584 --> 32:35.418
Do You Speak
Any Spanish At All?

32:35.419 --> 32:36.537
No.

32:36.538 --> 32:38.972
Well,
If You Want Me To,

32:38.973 --> 32:41.458
I Can Translate It
For You.

32:42.944 --> 32:46.130
If I Have Someone's Name,
Can I Get Hold Of Their Address?

32:46.131 --> 32:48.264
Yeah, Maybe.
There Are Street Guides,

32:48.265 --> 32:50.467
Information,
Phone Numbers.

32:50.468 --> 32:51.718
Would You Help Me?

32:51.719 --> 32:53.136
Yeah, Of Course
I Can But...

32:53.137 --> 32:55.789
Now I--I Really
Have To Finish This.

32:55.790 --> 32:57.691
Ok? When I Finish,

32:57.692 --> 32:59.375
I Can Translate
Everything For You,

32:59.376 --> 33:01.611
And We Can Meet Up.
What Do You Say?

33:01.612 --> 33:04.131
And What About Finding
That Woman's Address?

33:04.132 --> 33:06.833
Yeah, Well, That's Nothing.
Suppose We Could Try.

33:10.422 --> 33:14.942
Zoe? In Paris
With Susan?

33:14.943 --> 33:17.844
Cristy's On Her Way.

33:17.845 --> 33:21.298
She's Arriving
This Afternoon.

33:21.299 --> 33:23.783
We Want To Go
There Today.

33:26.020 --> 33:28.822
We Have To Go Back
To That Horrible Place

33:28.823 --> 33:31.274
If We Want To Know What
The Hell Is Going On.

33:34.528 --> 33:35.846
Sure.

33:37.632 --> 33:39.065
We'll Wait For You.

33:42.587 --> 33:44.287
Take Care Of Susan.

34:06.644 --> 34:08.610
[Muffled Voices]

34:17.655 --> 34:19.589
[Club Music Playing]

34:25.563 --> 34:27.547
He's Late.

34:27.547 --> 34:29.549
How Old Is He?

34:29.550 --> 34:31.051
Is He Hot?

34:31.052 --> 34:33.420
Look, I Just
Want The Translations.

34:33.420 --> 34:35.755
I Could Have
Translated It For You.

34:35.755 --> 34:38.391
So You Made Me Do All
This Work For Nothing?

34:38.391 --> 34:39.726
I'm Gabriel.

34:39.726 --> 34:40.744
Nice To Meet You.

34:40.745 --> 34:42.295
I'm Joel.
Hey.

34:42.295 --> 34:44.231
A Beer?
Uh, Cerveza?

34:44.232 --> 34:46.299
Oh, No. Thanks.
I Don't Drink.

34:46.300 --> 34:49.168
Eve Told Us You're
Studying History, Right?

34:49.168 --> 34:52.871
Well, Yes, It's Part
Of My Seminary Studies.

34:52.873 --> 34:55.574
Seminary?

34:55.576 --> 34:57.411
You Mean You...

34:57.412 --> 34:59.580
You Want
To Become A Priest?

34:59.581 --> 35:00.897
Gabriel: Yeah.

35:00.898 --> 35:02.499
You're Joking,
Aren't You?

35:02.500 --> 35:03.716
No.

35:03.717 --> 35:08.321
So, Have You Already
Taken The Vow Of Chastity?

35:08.322 --> 35:09.739
Joel, Stop It!

35:09.740 --> 35:11.741
That's Why You
Like Him, Isn't It?

35:11.742 --> 35:13.276
With Him,
You Feel Safe.

35:13.277 --> 35:14.261
She Knows--

35:14.262 --> 35:15.445
Shut The Fuck Up!

35:15.446 --> 35:18.598
Eve, I Think It Might
Be Better If I Leave.

35:18.599 --> 35:20.584
It's Been
A Pleasure.

35:20.585 --> 35:21.735
I'm Sorry!

35:21.736 --> 35:25.172
A Priest--
That's Funny!

35:30.244 --> 35:33.163
Wait! Um, I'm Really Sorry.
Joel Didn't Mean--

35:33.164 --> 35:35.165
You're So Stupid.

36:05.730 --> 36:06.747
[Club Music Playing]

36:06.748 --> 36:10.467
Materialism
And Spirituality...

36:10.468 --> 36:13.253
Each One Chooses
According To His Beliefs.

36:13.254 --> 36:14.804
Why Didn't You
Tell Me Before?

36:14.805 --> 36:16.339
You Know...

36:16.340 --> 36:17.658
Not Long Ago, I--

36:17.659 --> 36:19.493
I Wasn't So Different
From Your Friend Joel.

36:19.494 --> 36:23.080
I Thought The Most
Important Thing In Life...

36:23.081 --> 36:25.649
Was To Have
A Good Time.

36:25.650 --> 36:28.001
Parties, Alcohol...

36:28.002 --> 36:29.819
And Fun.

36:29.820 --> 36:33.857
Until My Girlfriend...

36:33.858 --> 36:36.259
Got Killed On
A Motorcycle Accident.

36:37.478 --> 36:39.446
I Was Driving.

36:41.482 --> 36:44.367
That Night
I Hadn't Drunk Anything,

36:44.368 --> 36:45.719
But Nobody Believed Me.

36:48.055 --> 36:50.190
And I Couldn't Stand It.

36:50.191 --> 36:52.375
[Club Music Playing]

36:55.546 --> 36:56.863
Thank You.

36:56.864 --> 36:58.181
Yes.

36:58.182 --> 37:00.083
How Come You're Interested
In This Religious School?

37:00.084 --> 37:01.718
My Mom Studied There.

37:01.719 --> 37:03.069
Well,
There's No Match.

37:03.070 --> 37:06.089
Here It Says It's
Been Closed Since 1988.

37:06.090 --> 37:07.474
Sister Ursula...

37:07.475 --> 37:08.691
Sister Ursula.

37:08.692 --> 37:12.044
The Principal--Disappeared
One Night, Same Year.

37:12.045 --> 37:14.013
So They Assumed
She Fled.

37:14.014 --> 37:15.982
Did You Get
That Lady's Address?

37:15.983 --> 37:17.634
This Is
Her Last Known Address.

37:44.678 --> 37:46.613
[Water Gurgling]

38:07.251 --> 38:09.219
[Dog Barks]

38:13.690 --> 38:15.108
Mambi?

38:19.346 --> 38:21.648
Mambi?

38:21.649 --> 38:23.316
[Club Music Playing]

38:26.537 --> 38:27.520
Let's Go.

38:29.524 --> 38:31.074
Where's Eve?

38:31.075 --> 38:33.243
I Don't Know. She
Told Me She Had To Leave.

38:33.244 --> 38:35.378
Shit. She Shouldn't
Have Gone Alone.

38:35.379 --> 38:36.429
Why?

38:36.430 --> 38:37.813
Hasn't She
Told You?

38:37.814 --> 38:40.049
No. What?

38:40.050 --> 38:41.818
Well...

38:41.819 --> 38:43.820
I Guess It Would Have
Been A Bit Embarrassing

38:43.821 --> 38:45.689
For Her To Tell
A Priest That...

38:45.690 --> 38:47.373
A Nun
Killed Her Mother.

38:47.374 --> 38:48.825
Hey, What Are You
Talking About?

38:48.826 --> 38:50.693
Do You Know
Where She Went?

38:50.694 --> 38:51.878
Yeah, I Think So.

38:51.879 --> 38:53.947
Ok, Let's Go.

39:20.074 --> 39:22.308
[Speaking Spanish]

39:51.522 --> 39:53.256
[Speaking Spanish]

39:54.508 --> 39:55.958
[Dog Whimpers]

40:02.132 --> 40:04.067
Mambi.

40:04.068 --> 40:05.385
[Whimpers]

40:05.386 --> 40:06.803
Mambi?

40:06.804 --> 40:09.422
[Speaking Spanish]

40:09.423 --> 40:10.573
Mambi?

40:10.574 --> 40:12.508
[Barking]

40:17.281 --> 40:20.299
[Barking]

40:20.300 --> 40:21.518
Mambi.

40:21.519 --> 40:22.502
Mambi.

41:03.210 --> 41:05.228
[Screams]

41:08.148 --> 41:10.316
Aah!

41:16.173 --> 41:18.107
Eulalia?

41:26.133 --> 41:28.684
I--I'm Eve,
Mary's Daughter.

41:28.685 --> 41:29.702
May I Come In?

41:33.057 --> 41:34.740
[Dog Whimpers]

41:37.895 --> 41:40.029
Eulalia?

42:07.591 --> 42:09.075
Aah! Oh!

42:09.076 --> 42:11.277
My God.
Gabriel!

42:11.278 --> 42:12.495
What Happened?

42:12.496 --> 42:14.597
Please, Guys,
Don't Look. Please.

42:19.653 --> 42:21.137
We Have To Call
The Police. Now!

42:21.138 --> 42:22.972
[Telephone Ringing]

42:28.962 --> 42:32.081
Answering Machine: Eulalia,
This Is Zoe. Are You There?

42:32.082 --> 42:34.667
We Were Delayed,
So We'll Be There Later.

42:34.668 --> 42:38.688
Susan's Been Hysterical Ever
Since I Told Her About Mary.

42:38.689 --> 42:40.590
Eulalia, If You Are
There, Please Pick Up.

42:42.627 --> 42:44.761
Susan Wants To Call
The Police, But We Can't.

42:44.762 --> 42:47.514
We Can't Call The Police
And You Know It.

42:47.515 --> 42:49.232
Eulalia, Cristy--

42:49.233 --> 42:50.549
This Is
A Fucking Nightmare.

42:50.550 --> 42:51.768
Where Are You Guys?

42:51.769 --> 42:54.787
Well, You're
Probably Gone By Now.

42:54.788 --> 42:58.624
Anyway, We'll Rent The Car
And Go Right To That Place.

42:58.625 --> 43:00.760
I Also Think The Answers
We Are Looking For

43:00.761 --> 43:02.545
Are Back
Where It All Began.

43:02.546 --> 43:04.480
[Machine Clicks Off]

43:10.388 --> 43:12.205
It's Gotta Be
Right Here Somewhere.

43:18.245 --> 43:21.598
You Know We
Should've Never Come.

43:21.599 --> 43:23.833
We Should've
Just Called The Cops.

43:23.834 --> 43:25.868
Gabriel: Listen,
Maybe Joel's Right.

43:25.869 --> 43:27.454
Maybe We Acted
Too Hastily.

43:30.774 --> 43:32.408
[Tires Squealing]

43:34.145 --> 43:35.111
Eve!

43:37.564 --> 43:39.081
We All Heard
The Answering Machine.

43:39.082 --> 43:40.783
We Have To Tell Them

43:40.784 --> 43:41.835
What Happened
To Cristy And Eulalia.

43:41.836 --> 43:43.419
They Are In Danger.

43:43.420 --> 43:46.606
Eve, Time Out
For A Second.

43:46.607 --> 43:49.108
Now, We Left
The Scene Of A Crime.

43:49.109 --> 43:50.944
Now, That Is A Crime
In Itself!

43:50.945 --> 43:53.046
God Damn It, Joel!

43:53.047 --> 43:54.881
I Told You Before,
If That's The Way You Feel,

43:54.882 --> 43:56.699
You Get Out Of The Car
And Call The Cops.

44:00.671 --> 44:02.188
Joel!

44:02.189 --> 44:04.840
Joel,
Don't Be Stupid!

44:04.841 --> 44:07.994
Eve...

44:07.995 --> 44:10.629
We're All Nervous.

44:10.630 --> 44:14.084
But Let's Try
To Be Reasonable, Ok?

44:14.085 --> 44:15.385
You Know What It's Like

44:15.386 --> 44:16.352
When No One
Believes You, Right?

44:16.353 --> 44:17.653
You've
Been There, Too.

44:20.224 --> 44:23.409
I Just Want To Find Out
What Happened To My Mother.

44:23.410 --> 44:24.761
I'm Sorry, Baby.

44:32.219 --> 44:34.653
Come On, Guys,
You Can't Stay Out Here.

44:38.458 --> 44:39.909
Look, What
Does It Say There?

44:45.916 --> 44:47.399
It Says They're Building

44:47.400 --> 44:49.568
Some Kind
Of Thermal Bathing Spa.

44:50.621 --> 44:52.922
[Thunder]

44:59.596 --> 45:01.931
There's A Turn Back There.
We Missed It.

45:01.932 --> 45:03.533
From Now On,
I'm Driving.

45:29.860 --> 45:32.095
Joel, Slow Down.
Please.

45:32.096 --> 45:34.847
I Just Want To Get
The Fuck There Already.

45:34.848 --> 45:36.683
Aah!

45:36.684 --> 45:37.800
Aah!

45:37.801 --> 45:39.319
Jesus.

45:39.320 --> 45:41.487
You Could
Have Killed Us!

45:41.488 --> 45:42.772
Well,
What's This...

45:42.773 --> 45:44.223
Fucking Car
Doing

45:44.224 --> 45:45.491
In The Middle
Of The Road?

45:48.395 --> 45:50.196
Damn It!

45:50.197 --> 45:52.131
[Engine Stalling]

45:55.619 --> 45:56.936
Shit.

45:56.937 --> 45:58.871
[Engine Stalling]

46:01.858 --> 46:03.142
There's No Coverage.

46:09.282 --> 46:10.767
Can You Start It?

46:10.768 --> 46:12.151
Gabriel: There's Nobody
Inside The Car.

46:12.152 --> 46:13.753
Eve: It's Got
To Be Theirs.

46:13.754 --> 46:16.089
Ok, But
It's Still Hot.

46:16.090 --> 46:17.673
It Won't Start.

46:20.894 --> 46:22.595
Look, Footprints.

46:22.596 --> 46:23.847
It's Them.

46:23.848 --> 46:27.033
Look! Let's Go!
Come On!

46:27.034 --> 46:28.083
Come On.

46:30.353 --> 46:31.570
Let's Go!

46:33.406 --> 46:34.590
Come On!

46:34.591 --> 46:35.674
Fine, Fine!

46:52.626 --> 46:54.577
Look, Guys.

46:54.578 --> 46:56.679
The Door's
Been Forced Open.

47:11.728 --> 47:13.730
Oh, Shit.

47:13.731 --> 47:15.080
You Should Have Taken

47:15.081 --> 47:16.332
The Scuba Flashlights
With Us.

47:16.333 --> 47:18.133
They're In The Car.

47:23.623 --> 47:25.041
Susan?

47:26.243 --> 47:27.893
Zoe?

47:27.894 --> 47:29.628
[Rumbling]

47:29.629 --> 47:31.664
What The Hell
Was That?

47:31.665 --> 47:32.948
I'll Have A Look.

47:42.576 --> 47:43.993
Welcome...

47:43.994 --> 47:46.946
To The Nun Witch Project.

47:53.270 --> 47:54.771
[Wings Flapping]

47:54.772 --> 47:56.573
Oh, Shit!

48:03.647 --> 48:05.681
What Was It?

48:05.682 --> 48:09.686
Birds. A Dirty Bathroom
Full Of Birds.

48:09.687 --> 48:12.388
They Must Have Flown In
Through The Broken Windows.

48:14.457 --> 48:17.059
Susan!

48:17.060 --> 48:18.561
Zoe!

48:34.794 --> 48:36.545
Hello?

48:40.483 --> 48:42.151
Zoe?

48:44.070 --> 48:45.938
Susan?

49:32.903 --> 49:34.904
Oh, Yeah.

49:34.905 --> 49:36.706
This Really
Is Some Place.

49:38.425 --> 49:43.145
This Is Exactly Where
I Want To Spend My Vacation.

49:43.146 --> 49:44.597
Stop Filming.

49:47.551 --> 49:49.485
I Don't Like
This Place.

49:52.523 --> 49:53.890
I'll Just...

50:02.599 --> 50:04.534
[Muffled Voices]

50:08.255 --> 50:09.905
There They Are.

50:24.487 --> 50:25.638
Sorry.

50:25.639 --> 50:27.306
And Eve?

50:27.307 --> 50:28.924
Uh...

50:28.925 --> 50:30.476
I Don't Know.

50:30.477 --> 50:31.744
We Lost Her.

50:33.914 --> 50:35.130
Eve!

50:35.131 --> 50:36.716
She's Not Here.

50:36.717 --> 50:37.900
Can't You See It?

50:37.901 --> 50:39.268
She's Not!

50:41.505 --> 50:42.821
And Eulalia.

50:42.822 --> 50:44.990
Where Are Cristy And
Eulalia, For God's Sake?

50:44.991 --> 50:46.308
Susan, Calm Down.

50:46.309 --> 50:48.243
Hello?

50:48.244 --> 50:49.595
Who Are You?

50:50.647 --> 50:51.997
I'm Eve.

50:51.998 --> 50:54.984
Mary O'brien's
Daughter.

50:54.985 --> 50:57.019
[Whispering]
What Is She Doing Here?

50:57.020 --> 50:58.604
Eve...

50:58.605 --> 51:00.740
I'm Zoe.

51:00.741 --> 51:02.241
And This Is--

51:02.242 --> 51:03.292
Susan.

51:06.096 --> 51:07.963
I'm Sorry.

51:07.964 --> 51:10.132
I'm So Sorry.

51:10.133 --> 51:12.334
Eulalia Told Us
About Your Mother.

51:12.335 --> 51:14.670
Eulalia
And Cristy

51:14.671 --> 51:16.305
Are Dead
As Well.

51:19.692 --> 51:22.528
Oh, God's Punishing Us.

51:22.529 --> 51:24.129
But When?

51:24.130 --> 51:25.965
Listen, We've--
We Have To Get Out Of Here

51:25.966 --> 51:27.115
And Call The Police.

51:27.116 --> 51:28.968
We Can't Waste
Any More Time.

51:28.969 --> 51:30.536
Please, Let Us
Get Out Of Here--

51:30.537 --> 51:32.054
Susan, We Can't
Call The Police.

51:32.055 --> 51:33.722
We Didn't
Do It Then,

51:33.723 --> 51:35.725
And We Won't
Do It Now,

51:35.726 --> 51:36.809
Understand?
Do You Understand?

51:40.630 --> 51:41.948
Did You Call Them?

51:43.217 --> 51:44.733
No.

51:46.837 --> 51:49.572
Why Can't We
Call The Police?

51:49.573 --> 51:52.124
I Know
Who Killed My Mother.

51:53.510 --> 51:55.310
It Was Her, The Nun,

51:55.311 --> 51:56.729
Sister Ursula.

51:56.730 --> 51:58.080
I Saw Her.

51:58.081 --> 51:59.682
I've Seen Her
With My Own Eyes.

51:59.683 --> 52:00.732
I Saw Her!

52:00.733 --> 52:01.984
No, I--I...

52:01.985 --> 52:03.920
I Don't Believe You.

52:03.921 --> 52:05.938
That Can't Be True.

52:05.939 --> 52:08.557
Can It, Zoe?

52:08.558 --> 52:09.875
Why?

52:11.444 --> 52:13.162
Go On, Tell Her!

52:13.163 --> 52:14.797
Tell Her!

52:14.798 --> 52:16.248
It Can't Be Her.

52:16.249 --> 52:17.399
Shut Up.

52:18.518 --> 52:20.953
It Can't Be
Sister Ursula.

52:20.954 --> 52:22.521
That's
Impossible.

52:22.522 --> 52:24.589
Why Is That Impossible?

52:26.343 --> 52:28.110
Because...

52:28.111 --> 52:29.528
She's Dead...

52:31.264 --> 52:32.881
[Whispering]
Dead.

52:45.795 --> 52:47.013
Mmm.

52:50.133 --> 52:51.216
There You Are!

52:52.719 --> 52:54.403
What Are You
Up To Now?

52:55.488 --> 52:56.772
Are You Crazy?!

52:56.773 --> 52:57.957
Aah!

52:57.958 --> 53:00.709
Why Is It That You
Always Do The Wrong Thing?

53:00.710 --> 53:02.644
<i>Eulalia: Why Is It
That You're Always</i>

53:02.645 --> 53:04.713
Complaining
About Everything?

53:04.714 --> 53:06.231
Where's Mary?

53:06.232 --> 53:08.133
Why Isn't
She With You?

53:08.134 --> 53:09.818
She's Not In Her Room.

53:09.819 --> 53:12.304
Girl:
Stop! Stop!

53:12.305 --> 53:13.655
Stop!

53:13.656 --> 53:15.591
It's Coming From
The Downstairs Bathroom.

53:15.592 --> 53:17.660
That's Mary's Voice.

53:27.454 --> 53:30.222
[Mary Yelling]

53:31.991 --> 53:33.476
What Are You Doing?!

53:33.477 --> 53:35.995
Purifying Her!
Purifying.

53:35.996 --> 53:37.946
She's Going
To Kill Her!

53:39.315 --> 53:41.817
Stop It!

53:41.818 --> 53:43.368
You Fucking Bitch!
Leave Her Alone!

53:44.837 --> 53:45.955
Get Away!

53:45.956 --> 53:48.457
Susan! Help Her!

53:48.458 --> 53:50.392
Help Me!

53:50.393 --> 53:52.044
[All Shouting]

53:57.067 --> 53:58.283
Oh, My God.

54:03.639 --> 54:06.108
[Ragged Breathing]

54:14.151 --> 54:15.401
[All Scream]

54:17.637 --> 54:19.338
Stop,
Don't Kill Her!

54:39.392 --> 54:40.709
This Pond...

54:40.710 --> 54:43.562
It's Supposed To Be
Holy Water, Remember?

54:43.563 --> 54:47.866
The Nuns From The Convent
Purify Themselves Here.

54:47.867 --> 54:52.037
Shit. It's Just
A Normal Fucking Pond.

54:52.038 --> 54:54.573
We've Got To Swear
That We Never,

54:54.574 --> 54:57.826
Ever Tell Anyone
What We've Done

54:57.827 --> 55:00.095
Or What
Happened Here Tonight.

55:11.758 --> 55:12.774
Susan.

55:25.071 --> 55:27.539
[Whispering] Hail Mary,
Full Of Grace...

55:55.134 --> 55:56.786
This Is Crazy.

55:56.787 --> 55:58.421
It's Fucking Crazy!

55:58.422 --> 56:00.255
Take It Easy,
Joel. Come On.

56:00.256 --> 56:02.074
And What Do You
Expect Me To Do

56:02.075 --> 56:03.976
After What
I've Just Heard?

56:03.977 --> 56:05.810
Look, We Should Just
Go To The Nearest Town

56:05.811 --> 56:07.062
And Call The Cops.

56:07.063 --> 56:09.732
The Nearest Town Is
10 Miles Away, Remember?

56:09.733 --> 56:12.384
And We Shouldn't Leave
Them Hanging Here Alone.

56:16.172 --> 56:17.739
I'm Afraid We're The Ones

56:17.740 --> 56:20.409
Who Are Gonna Be
Hung For Being Here.

56:20.410 --> 56:21.827
[Thunder]

56:21.828 --> 56:23.662
It Can't Be True.

56:23.663 --> 56:26.781
My Mother
Never Hurt Anyone.

56:26.782 --> 56:28.517
Why Would
Sister Ursula Want

56:28.518 --> 56:29.602
To Kill My Mother?

56:30.853 --> 56:32.604
Why?

56:32.605 --> 56:33.839
Because She Was--

56:33.840 --> 56:35.491
She Was Crazy.

56:35.492 --> 56:37.226
She Said
That Her Mission Was

56:37.227 --> 56:39.178
To End With All
The Sin In The World

56:39.179 --> 56:41.280
Through
Punishment And Pain.

56:43.933 --> 56:45.283
Maybe
She Didn't Die,

56:45.284 --> 56:46.335
And Now
She's Come Back

56:46.336 --> 56:47.519
To Seek
Her Revenge.

56:47.520 --> 56:49.388
But Why Now,
After 18 Years?

56:49.389 --> 56:50.839
Why Did She
Wait So Long?

56:50.840 --> 56:52.274
The Pond Water...

56:55.378 --> 56:57.513
They Used To Say It Was...

56:57.514 --> 56:59.748
Holy Water.

56:59.749 --> 57:00.983
Can't You See?

57:02.702 --> 57:05.720
The People From The
Thermal Bathing Spa

57:05.721 --> 57:08.941
Dried Out The Pond
2 Weeks Ago.

57:08.942 --> 57:10.975
They Told Us
That In Town.

57:10.976 --> 57:12.361
You Told Me
Joanna Died

57:12.362 --> 57:14.062
Exactly 2 Weeks Ago.

57:15.882 --> 57:18.183
When The Pond
Water Disappeared,

57:18.184 --> 57:20.119
Her Spirit
Was Set Free.

57:22.555 --> 57:24.222
It Won't
Rest In Peace

57:24.223 --> 57:25.891
Until She's Completed
Her Mission,

57:25.892 --> 57:27.109
Remember?

57:27.110 --> 57:28.760
Come On, Susan, Stop!

57:28.761 --> 57:29.778
Shut Up!

57:29.779 --> 57:30.929
Ok?

57:30.930 --> 57:32.047
Ok?

57:32.048 --> 57:34.216
So, Let Me Get
This Straight,

57:34.217 --> 57:37.035
Are You Trying
To Tell Me That All This

57:37.036 --> 57:39.070
Is Some Sort Of...

57:39.071 --> 57:41.106
<i>I Know What You
Did 18 Summers Ago,</i>

57:41.107 --> 57:42.191
Or Something?

57:43.743 --> 57:44.893
Oh, Shit.

57:44.894 --> 57:45.911
I Don't Know
