01:16:51.156 --> 01:16:54.958
Stop Crying,
You Stupid Child.

01:16:54.959 --> 01:16:57.294
I'm Going
To Cleanse You.

01:16:57.295 --> 01:16:58.846
No! No!

01:16:58.847 --> 01:16:59.997
Ohh!

01:16:59.998 --> 01:17:01.933
[Screaming]

01:17:05.020 --> 01:17:06.921
Him?

01:17:06.922 --> 01:17:08.205
Who Was My Father?

01:17:10.642 --> 01:17:13.277
Tell Me!

01:17:13.278 --> 01:17:15.413
Your Mother Made Us Swear
That We Would--

01:17:15.414 --> 01:17:17.965
My Mother Is Dead.

01:17:17.966 --> 01:17:20.568
She's Dead.

01:17:20.569 --> 01:17:22.069
Who Was He?

01:17:26.442 --> 01:17:29.860
You Cannot Stand
These Confessions.

01:17:29.861 --> 01:17:31.378
For It Was A Priest.

01:17:31.379 --> 01:17:32.880
Father Miguel.

01:17:35.250 --> 01:17:36.266
Miguel?

01:17:36.267 --> 01:17:38.435
A Priest? And
Sister Ursula Knew?

01:17:38.436 --> 01:17:39.754
She Won't Rest

01:17:39.755 --> 01:17:42.289
Until She's Killed Everyone
Who Was Here That Night.

01:17:45.510 --> 01:17:46.944
What Can We Do?

01:17:46.945 --> 01:17:49.379
The Spear
Didn't Work.

01:17:49.380 --> 01:17:53.066
You Can't Kill
A Ghost With A Spear.

01:17:53.067 --> 01:17:55.569
<i>If That Thing
Was A Ghost.</i>

01:17:55.570 --> 01:17:57.571
Dust You Are...

01:17:57.572 --> 01:18:00.824
And To Dust
You Shall Return.

01:18:00.825 --> 01:18:03.160
Sister Ursula Died
In The Water.

01:18:03.161 --> 01:18:04.829
Eve Says There's
Always Water.

01:18:04.830 --> 01:18:07.031
She Appears, Always,
Through Water.

01:18:07.032 --> 01:18:08.382
She Needs Water
To Exist.

01:18:08.383 --> 01:18:10.751
To Take On
A Physical Form.

01:18:10.752 --> 01:18:13.236
If She Can Kill
In The Water,

01:18:13.237 --> 01:18:15.439
In The Water,
She Can Die.

01:18:15.440 --> 01:18:17.308
What Do You Mean?
That If We Manage To Make

01:18:17.309 --> 01:18:18.959
That Thing Appear
In The Water,

01:18:18.960 --> 01:18:20.478
We Could Shoot It?

01:18:20.479 --> 01:18:22.313
Under The Water,
We Have A Chance.

01:18:22.314 --> 01:18:23.981
We Have To Take Her

01:18:23.982 --> 01:18:25.332
To A Place That We
Can Flood.

01:18:25.333 --> 01:18:27.601
In The Water, She'll
Become Flesh And Blood.

01:18:31.289 --> 01:18:32.823
Where?

01:18:32.824 --> 01:18:33.907
I Know.

01:18:39.097 --> 01:18:41.398
I Have No Intention
Of Being Buried Today.

01:18:43.535 --> 01:18:44.852
Do You Hear Me?

01:18:44.853 --> 01:18:46.887
Fucking Slut!

01:18:46.888 --> 01:18:48.239
The Main Faucet
Must Be Closed.

01:18:48.240 --> 01:18:50.474
There Were Some Water
Tanks On The Top Floor.

01:18:50.475 --> 01:18:51.592
I'll Try To Open Them.

01:18:53.762 --> 01:18:54.912
Be Careful.

01:18:56.614 --> 01:18:58.215
I'm Coming
With You.

01:18:58.216 --> 01:18:59.383
Let's Plug The Drains.

01:18:59.384 --> 01:19:00.601
Eve: With What?

01:19:00.602 --> 01:19:01.719
With These?

01:19:01.720 --> 01:19:03.087
We Need More.

01:19:03.088 --> 01:19:04.104
In The Kitchen,

01:19:04.105 --> 01:19:05.088
There Must Be
Some More Rags.

01:19:05.089 --> 01:19:06.107
I'll Go
Get Them.

01:19:06.108 --> 01:19:07.074
Wait. Don't
Go Alone.

01:19:07.075 --> 01:19:08.092
No, No, No.
I'll Go With You.

01:19:08.093 --> 01:19:09.010
Julia, She Won't Hurt You.

01:19:21.957 --> 01:19:23.274
Ok.

01:19:23.275 --> 01:19:26.393
These Must Be
The Main Water Tanks.

01:19:26.394 --> 01:19:27.712
Let's Open
All The Faucets.

01:19:27.713 --> 01:19:29.313
Come On.

01:19:29.314 --> 01:19:30.731
What Are We
Doing Up Here?

01:19:36.054 --> 01:19:38.705
This Is
A Waste Of Time.

01:19:38.706 --> 01:19:40.224
And I Know
You Don't Believe

01:19:40.225 --> 01:19:41.675
Any Of This
Ghost Crap, Either.

01:19:47.749 --> 01:19:49.066
You And Eve--

01:19:49.067 --> 01:19:51.569
You Don't Understand
Anything, Joel.

01:19:58.160 --> 01:19:59.243
Eve:
They Made It.

01:19:59.244 --> 01:20:00.461
We Have To Go.

01:20:00.462 --> 01:20:01.645
She's By Herself.

01:20:15.944 --> 01:20:17.128
[Ghostly Whisper]

01:20:50.812 --> 01:20:52.296
[Creaking]

01:20:55.450 --> 01:20:56.467
Aah!

01:21:01.890 --> 01:21:03.073
It Won't Fucking Close!

01:21:12.333 --> 01:21:13.984
Gabriel?

01:21:23.511 --> 01:21:25.579
[Pipes Clanking]

01:21:35.723 --> 01:21:36.690
Unh!

01:21:47.786 --> 01:21:48.969
And Zoe?

01:21:48.970 --> 01:21:50.654
Right Behind Me.
Come On.

01:21:50.655 --> 01:21:51.972
We Have To Plug
All The Drains.

01:21:54.292 --> 01:21:55.409
Yes.

01:21:57.262 --> 01:21:58.179
Here.

01:22:04.118 --> 01:22:05.835
Gabriel,
Can You Hear Me?

01:22:14.479 --> 01:22:16.447
I'm Getting Nervous.

01:22:16.448 --> 01:22:18.382
Where Are They?

01:22:23.054 --> 01:22:24.688
[Electricity Crackling]

01:22:35.967 --> 01:22:36.917
What The Fuck Was That?

01:22:36.918 --> 01:22:38.569
The Electricity's
Been Wet.

01:22:38.570 --> 01:22:40.337
Looks Like Joel
Messed It Up.

01:22:40.338 --> 01:22:43.090
Zoe's Taking Too Long.
I'd Better Go Find Her.

01:22:43.091 --> 01:22:44.241
No, No.

01:22:44.242 --> 01:22:45.926
I Know You Are
The Only One

01:22:45.927 --> 01:22:47.528
Who Can See Her
If She Comes.

01:23:15.773 --> 01:23:17.274
[Clanking
And Creaking]

01:23:35.343 --> 01:23:36.760
[Screaming]

01:23:43.334 --> 01:23:46.286
[Rumbling]

01:23:55.430 --> 01:23:57.497
Zoe!

01:23:57.498 --> 01:23:58.699
Zoe!

01:24:01.018 --> 01:24:02.319
Zoe!

01:24:10.544 --> 01:24:11.945
[Gasps]

01:24:13.632 --> 01:24:15.432
[Thunder]

01:24:23.491 --> 01:24:25.276
[Clatter]

01:24:25.277 --> 01:24:26.677
Joel.

01:24:26.678 --> 01:24:28.445
Joel!

01:25:14.025 --> 01:25:15.309
No.

01:25:15.310 --> 01:25:17.911
No.

01:25:17.912 --> 01:25:19.980
We Can't Do Anything
For Her Anymore.

01:25:24.585 --> 01:25:25.686
Grr!

01:25:27.956 --> 01:25:29.673
[Buzzing]

01:25:32.010 --> 01:25:34.394
At Last!

01:25:34.395 --> 01:25:35.745
Joel Fixed It.

01:25:37.782 --> 01:25:39.199
Shit.

01:25:39.200 --> 01:25:41.302
The Water
Is Higher Now.

01:25:46.258 --> 01:25:47.874
If The Water
Touches The Lamp,

01:25:47.875 --> 01:25:48.992
We'll
Be Electrocuted.

01:26:16.171 --> 01:26:18.955
The Drain--I'm
Draining The Water.

01:26:18.956 --> 01:26:20.958
Get Out
Of The Water.

01:26:20.959 --> 01:26:22.108
No.

01:26:22.109 --> 01:26:24.128
If She Attacks Me
Out Of The Water,

01:26:24.129 --> 01:26:26.646
I Won't Be Able
To Do Anything.

01:26:26.647 --> 01:26:29.016
This Is
The Only Chance.

01:26:29.017 --> 01:26:31.802
You Go And Turn Off
The Electricity, Ok?

01:26:31.803 --> 01:26:32.887
Ok.

01:26:32.888 --> 01:26:34.071
Turn It Off.

01:26:55.310 --> 01:26:57.778
Joel! Gabriel!

01:27:40.655 --> 01:27:42.689
Eve?

01:27:42.690 --> 01:27:44.340
Eve?

01:27:47.945 --> 01:27:49.062
Eve?

01:27:52.316 --> 01:27:53.566
I Knew
You Could Do It.

01:27:53.567 --> 01:27:54.651
You Ok? Now What?

01:27:57.605 --> 01:27:59.906
She's Coming.

01:27:59.907 --> 01:28:02.543
But She's
Coming For Me.

01:28:02.544 --> 01:28:04.511
Julia, You're Gonna
Have To Leave Now.

01:28:10.000 --> 01:28:11.251
I'm Gonna Be Ok.

01:28:16.841 --> 01:28:18.175
Good Luck.

01:28:46.971 --> 01:28:48.572
[Sighs]

01:29:20.321 --> 01:29:22.423
[Ghostly Whisper]

01:29:57.392 --> 01:29:58.508
[Gasps]

01:30:00.745 --> 01:30:01.995
Are You Ok?

01:30:01.996 --> 01:30:03.146
Yes.

01:30:03.147 --> 01:30:04.164
Yes!

01:30:04.165 --> 01:30:05.465
It's You.

01:30:10.338 --> 01:30:12.873
Gabriel's Gone.

01:30:12.874 --> 01:30:15.792
There Has Been
An Accident.

01:30:15.793 --> 01:30:17.461
And Zoe Is Dead, Too!

01:30:20.397 --> 01:30:21.698
Listen.

01:30:21.699 --> 01:30:24.200
I Think I Have
An Explanation For All This.

01:30:24.201 --> 01:30:26.336
No, No.
It's Not The Time.

01:30:26.337 --> 01:30:28.371
Eve Is In Danger.

01:30:28.372 --> 01:30:31.925
No. It's Not Eve
That Is In Danger.

01:30:31.926 --> 01:30:34.661
Julia, Please. Just Sit
Down For A Moment.

01:30:43.337 --> 01:30:44.671
[Gasps]

01:31:01.739 --> 01:31:04.124
Were You There
When Zoe Died?

01:31:04.125 --> 01:31:06.793
No.

01:31:06.794 --> 01:31:10.763
She Went With Eve And--

01:31:10.764 --> 01:31:12.348
And Never Came Back.

01:31:17.839 --> 01:31:20.006
Just Like Susan.

01:31:20.007 --> 01:31:21.607
And...

01:31:21.608 --> 01:31:23.293
Cristy.

01:31:23.294 --> 01:31:25.779
Eulalia.

01:31:25.780 --> 01:31:27.363
And Mary.

01:31:29.800 --> 01:31:31.868
You Stupid Brat!

01:31:31.869 --> 01:31:32.952
Keep Out Of My Things.

01:31:32.953 --> 01:31:33.970
[Telephone Rings]

01:31:33.971 --> 01:31:35.288
These Are Mine.
[Ring]

01:31:35.289 --> 01:31:37.123
Do You Hear Me?

01:31:37.124 --> 01:31:37.941
Mine!
[Ring]

01:31:37.942 --> 01:31:39.059
Miguel?

01:31:39.060 --> 01:31:40.961
When I Was Alone
With Gabriel,

01:31:40.962 --> 01:31:42.278
He Told Me
Something.

01:31:42.279 --> 01:31:43.730
Where Are You?
At The Airport?

01:31:43.731 --> 01:31:45.199
Joel: Eve Started
To Remember Things

01:31:45.200 --> 01:31:47.600
From When She Was
A Little Girl.

01:31:47.601 --> 01:31:50.654
Ok. Eve's Mother Tried
To Commit Suicide.

01:31:50.655 --> 01:31:51.805
And?

01:31:51.806 --> 01:31:54.074
Eve Told Gabriel

01:31:54.075 --> 01:31:55.992
That Her Mother
Tried To Kill Herself

01:31:55.993 --> 01:31:57.293
Because
She Couldn't Cope

01:31:57.294 --> 01:32:00.580
With The Murder She
Committed 18 Years Ago.

01:32:00.581 --> 01:32:01.832
Here, In This Place.

01:32:01.833 --> 01:32:03.183
I Killed Her
Because I Fucked You!

01:32:03.184 --> 01:32:05.452
Do You Understand?

01:32:05.453 --> 01:32:06.803
Eve Knew All Along

01:32:06.804 --> 01:32:09.790
That Her Mother
Had Killed A Nun.

01:32:09.791 --> 01:32:10.974
What's Wrong, Mom?

01:32:10.975 --> 01:32:12.575
Aah!

01:32:16.848 --> 01:32:18.565
The Only Explanation

01:32:18.566 --> 01:32:21.651
I Can Come Up With...

01:32:21.652 --> 01:32:26.506
Is That Eve's Brain...

01:32:26.507 --> 01:32:28.841
Must Have...

01:32:28.842 --> 01:32:30.877
Blocked Out
That Part Of Her Memory.

01:32:30.878 --> 01:32:32.762
Mom!
Mom, Wake Up!

01:32:32.763 --> 01:32:35.816
And Now...

01:32:35.817 --> 01:32:38.335
Something Must
Have Brought It Back.

01:32:45.993 --> 01:32:47.677
Aah!

01:32:53.518 --> 01:32:55.268
Aah!

01:32:55.269 --> 01:32:56.619
What The Hell
Do You Mean?

01:32:59.240 --> 01:33:01.174
Ok.

01:33:01.175 --> 01:33:02.692
We Both Know

01:33:02.693 --> 01:33:05.195
That Eve Was
The Only Person Present

01:33:05.196 --> 01:33:06.796
At The Scene
Of The Crimes.

01:33:09.032 --> 01:33:10.550
Yeah, And?

01:33:10.551 --> 01:33:12.786
She's The Only One
Who Could Have Done It.

01:33:18.759 --> 01:33:19.910
Leave Me Alone.

01:33:19.911 --> 01:33:21.661
You're Responsible
For All This.

01:33:21.662 --> 01:33:22.796
Susan!

01:33:30.070 --> 01:33:32.556
Joel: Somehow,
The Nun Lived Through Eve,

01:33:32.557 --> 01:33:35.458
Possessed Her
Like Some Curse.

01:33:35.459 --> 01:33:37.226
[Screams]

01:33:39.763 --> 01:33:40.981
Eve!

01:34:06.741 --> 01:34:08.024
[Roaring]

01:34:09.309 --> 01:34:10.260
Unh!

01:34:25.793 --> 01:34:29.545
This Is The Truth
About The Nun.

01:34:29.546 --> 01:34:33.200
Eve And The Nun Are
The Same Person.

01:35:39.383 --> 01:35:42.551
[Singing In Spanish]

01:36:06.610 --> 01:36:09.546
[Singing Continues]

01:37:06.620 --> 01:37:09.539
[Singing Continues]

01:38:38.279 --> 01:38:41.230
[Samba Music Playing]

01:39:38.305 --> 01:39:41.207
[Samba Continues]
